### Environment variable usage
# Uses {{baseUrl}}, {{token}}, {{version}} from the active environment

# @name listUsers
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{version}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Shared variable access
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{version}}/info
X-Api-Version: {{apiVersion}}
X-Shared-Key: {{sharedKey}}

###

### Mixed file + env vars
@endpoint = /users/me

GET {{baseUrl}}{{endpoint}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### System vars in body
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{version}}/events
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_id": "{{$guid}}",
  "timestamp": "{{$timestamp}}",
  "type": "login",
  "user_count": {{$randomInt 1 1000}}
}
